Content:: This is a list of the buildings, sites, districts, and objects listed on the National Register of Historic Places across the United States Minor Outlying Islands. There are currently two listed sites located on two of the twelve islands or atolls that make up the Minor Outlying Islands.     This National Park Service list is complete through NPS recent listings posted July 15, 2022.[1]
